{"tid":505204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麥明詩fb上載警方回信闢謠 證真有其事確曾報警","createTime":"2017-12-21T00:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T12:20:12.000Z","uid":66943,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7b201b5e0674e5b19b46fbc6de0ebdb1257f6307","tid":505204,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T00:56:02.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171221/57607662\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171221%2F57607662&d=Lae4Q969r7wfmezT87%2Byq10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=20d52628\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171221%2F57607662&h=9b14c639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171221/57607662</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171221/large/1513785803_aaa8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171221%2Flarge%2F1513785803_aaa8.png&h=a6e47edc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港隊「欄后」呂麗瑤月初在fb公開聲稱多年前曾遭教練性侵，無綫藝人麥明詩事隔兩日亦在其fb表示有類似經歷，並分享遇事女性在法律下可以如何更好保障自己，但隨即惹網民質疑事件真偽，指麥企圖「抽水」，引發另一場口舌之爭。<br />\n<br />\n麥明詩今晚在fb再行上載一封香港警方於本月17日發出的回信，信中提及麥在今個月5日去信警方，要求取得當年的報案資料，惟警方稱該宗於2012年8月13日在長沙灣警署的報案，案件資料包括證人供詞等，已於2013年11月1日銷毀，故無法提供相關內容。即使警方未能提供細節，但信件已反映警方有備存報案記錄，亦間接證實了麥明詩當年確實曾向警方報案。"},{"pid":"d5b5c011a8f5c9a7d5655b0aecb3f2859432b124","tid":505204,"uid":107927,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T00:56:59.000Z","msg":"咁呂麗瑤報左警未"},{"pid":"3826b5d251a1ecc26e8f1bae3663040a434097dc","tid":505204,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T02:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be6b3c28751b719f14c9fd3f010394cd3bae2bf","tid":505204,"uid":111253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T02:15:00.000Z","msg":"闢<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">瑤</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1451e254355c5a4688b717f5c722947fabde29aa","tid":505204,"uid":15815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T03:13:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁呂麗瑤報左警未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n似係公審完就算數🤷🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n告到坐監又有咩so 先<br />\n唔報警以後仲有計傾<br />\n條女計數幾醒👍"},{"pid":"b8ee0c6a84d09d4eb2f368e875a06b378137061d","tid":505204,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T09:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4111f13a2903f2e1e4ccfd9b656a0094618cba","tid":505204,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}